            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white p-3 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
              <div class="bg-green-100 p-2 rounded-full flex-shrink-0">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-green-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 11.5V14m0-2.5v-6a1.5 1.5 0 113 0m-3 6a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0v2a7.5 7.5 0 0015 0v-5a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m-6-3V11m0-5.5v-1a1.5 1.5 0 013 0v1m0 0V11m0-5.5a1.5 1.5 0 013 0v3m0 0V11" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="font-medium">Для участков с густой растительностью: 0,75 л на 1 га (род Ixodes)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white p-3 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
              <div class="bg-green-100 p-2 rounded-full flex-shrink-0">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-green-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
